greeting_foreign: Sedit qui timuit ne non succederet.
translation_en: He who feared that he would not succeed sat still.

greeting_foreign: Ogni giorno è un nuovo inizio.
translation_en: Every day is a new beginning.

greeting_foreign: Maak er een mooie dag van.

translation_en: Go hard! / Give it your all!
Keep it up! / Go for it!
It will all work out in the end.
Have a nice rest of the day!
May it be easy (said to someone working).
I wish you a nice day.

greeting_foreign: Is féidir leat é a dhéanamh.

translation_en: Keep at it / Don't give up.

greeting_foreign: O lona uiga o le lalolagi.
You are capable of amazing things.
translation_en: You are capable of amazing things.

greeting_foreign: Va au bout de tes rêves.
translation_en: Go to the end of your dreams.
